Scenario.UserTask: You are Brian White and would like to report fraud on your bank account. Somebody has transferred $500 from your account.. Unfortunately, you don't remember your account number nor your PIN. Your date of birth is 25/03/1998. For your security questions, your mother's maiden name is Wong and your childhood pet is Molly.

UserQuestionnaire.Question: Did the AI Assistant succesfully report fraud on your account?
Did the AI Assistant stay calm and helpful throughout the dialogue?

Did the user become aggressive or annoyed during the dialogue? (Note: some users may be instructed to be annoying.)
